data.description: Rare Find! 5BR/3BTH/2CG  2-story home, corner lot, fenced & over 1/4 acres! ROOF 2021! AC 2019! This beautiful home has custom paint, new chair rails, tile & laminate floors! Gorgeous kitchen with island, ss appliances, & pantry! Formal dining room off the foyer entrance! Elegant lighting & ceiling fans throughout! Spacious family room! Guest bedroom & bath 1st floor along with laundry room! 2nd flr. features loft/5th bedroom, 2 additional bedrooms & guest bath! Luxury awaits in your oversized primary owner's suite w/his/her closets, & large primary bath w/sep. shower/sep. garden tub! New Epoxy garage floor! Gorgeous homes in surrounding area, no HOA! Bring the pets, toys, RV & boat! Plenty of room for a pool!! Centrally located and close to 95 & FL TPKE for commuter's delight!
